@startuml
object Scheduler
object "Voice attendance sync" as VoiceAttendanceSync
object "Discord voice API" as DiscordVoiceAPI
object "Attendance storage" as AttendanceStorage
object "Session finance sync" as SessionFinanceSync
object "Finance storage" as FinanceStorage
object "Open sessions" as OpenSessions <<database>>
object "Student Discord credentials" as StudentDiscordCredentials <<database>>
object Attendance <<database>>
object "Fee records" as FeeRecords <<database>>
Scheduler --> VoiceAttendanceSync : 1: run loop
VoiceAttendanceSync --> OpenSessions : 2: find open sessions
VoiceAttendanceSync --> DiscordVoiceAPI : 3: collect voice identities
DiscordVoiceAPI --> VoiceAttendanceSync : 4: voice identities
VoiceAttendanceSync --> StudentDiscordCredentials : 5: load enrolled credentials
VoiceAttendanceSync --> AttendanceStorage : 6: mark present if not manual
AttendanceStorage --> Attendance : 7: INSERT/UPDATE
VoiceAttendanceSync --> SessionFinanceSync : 8: sync charge
SessionFinanceSync --> FinanceStorage : 9: write Fee record
FinanceStorage --> FeeRecords : 10: UPSERT
VoiceAttendanceSync --> Scheduler : 11: complete
@enduml
